sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as ElysiaJS
    participant A as Agent
    participant L as LLM

    C->>S: POST /api/chat
    S->>A: invoke(message)
    A->>L: stream(prompt)
    loop Token Streaming
        L-->>A: token
        A-->>S: token
        S-->>C: SSE data: token
    end
    S-->>C: SSE data: citations
    S-->>C: SSE data: done
